<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الرجز]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَابِي الْحُيُودِ فَارِضِ الْحُنْجُورِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">حَابِي يَقُولُ:</span> مُشْرِفٌ وَالحْيُودُ: كُلُّ عَضَلَةٍ شَاخِصَةٍ عَنِ الْجِلْدِ وَفَارِضٌ: ضَخْمٌ وَالْحُنْجُورُ: الْحَنْجَرَةُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>